Manic Magazine - February 2014

152 Pages | HQ PDF | English | 54 MB 


MANIC is not just a magazine, it is an ULTIMATE GUIDEBOOK FOR MODERN MEN. MANIC brings you inspirational, intelligent and, above all, fun-to-read articles, as well as breathtaking photography, and priceless tips & tricks. MANIC will give you advice on how to look the best, live the healthiest, and be the most successful.
